<sec>
<st>
History</st>
<p>

Started in <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../234/67234.xml">
Newark, New Jersey</link></village>
 in 1875, Prudential Financial, Inc. as it is known today, was originally called the "The Widows and Orphans Friendly Society" and was founded by <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
<person wordnetid="100007846" confidence="0.8">
<social_event wordnetid="107288639" confidence="0.8">
<ceremony wordnetid="107450842" confidence="0.8">
<lawgiver wordnetid="110249270" confidence="0.8">
<burial wordnetid="107451687" confidence="0.8">
